oid;\n+  setTitle(title: string): void;\n+  on(event: \'close\' | \'show\' | \'h
ide\', callback: () => void): this;\n+}\n+```\n+\n+**动画规格：**\n+- `show`：`a
lpha 0→1`，`scale 0.8→1`，`duration=250`，`ease=\'Back.out\'`。\n+- `hide`：`alp
ha 1→0`，`scale 1→0.8`，`duration=200`，`ease=\'Power2\'`。\n+\n+---\n+\n+### 4.
2 UIButton — 通用按钮\n+\n+**资源映射：**\n+- 底图：`base-btn.png`（通用按钮）、
`base-edit.png`（编辑态特殊按钮）。\n+- 无文字底图需配合 Phaser `Text` 使用。\n+
\n+**接口设计：**\n+\n+```typescript\n+export interface UIButtonConfig {\n+  x: 
number;\n+  y: number;\n+  width?: number;\n+  height?: number;\n+  texture?: st
ring;        // 如 \'base-btn\', \'base-edit\'\n+  text?: string;\n+  textStyle?
